{"tid":174611,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發：新政上場 清算傘運】","createTime":"2017-03-27T02:53:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-27T02:57:01.000Z","uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d1ff72fe7367819aab0736bdfead4055572a58be","tid":174611,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T02:53:05.000Z","msg":"今早學聯前常委鍾耀華、張秀賢均接到警方電話，因雨傘運動而被控以「公眾妨擾罪」，今日將到灣仔警署被捕。針對雨傘運動的清算將會繼續，預計被捕及被落案起訴的核心組織者將會陸續增加。<br />\n<br />\n消息將持續更新，希望各同路人能到場聲援。<br />\n<br />\n其他已知被控人士：佔中三子、黃浩銘、陳淑莊議員、邵家臻議員<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/pg/NathanLawKC/posts/?ref=page_internal\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpg%2FNathanLawKC%2Fposts%2F%3Fref%3Dpage_internal&d=ZU5rKlsKhNp37FgV%2FTwvgsmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=0a8d26cc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/pg/NathanLawKC/posts/?ref=page_internal</a>"},{"pid":"6194f0c34588eb6aca34cf36992c9d3bbc4ce8df","tid":174611,"uid":8493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T02:53:59.000Z","msg":"開始清算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"036d60af4a18650a6fa7880134117128fb897c77","tid":174611,"uid":64966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T02:57:01.000Z","msg":"正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}